parameters:
Haa... Haa... Hang in there! We're almost there,
just a little bit more.

Yes... Thanks to you, I've started to be able to
walk a little.

Rat spotted! You really did a number on us last
time!
Damn it! They've caught up! We were so close!

You won't escape! We'll defeat you here and redeem
our previous disgrace!

Esuka! Are you okay⁉ I'm heading your way with our
allies!
I'm fine! I'll beat the crap out of them!
Fuhahaha! What's the matter, is it over already?

(This is bad, it's still going to take time to get
reinforcements)

Shuu! Don't worry! I'll find an opening and escape
with this person!

...If it's just Esuka, there's a high chance she
can escape.

No! Absolutely not! I won't do such a thing! I can
still keep going!

※A choice will appear after this. Do you want to
save? (Depending on your choice, it may result in
a game over)
Shuu! Don't make me say it over and over!

Enough chatter... If you won't come, then we'll
come to you!

Damn! What is this strength! My regeneration can't
keep up‼
Stop it, Esuka! You can't take any more!

Ha...ha...I'm sorry... I'll buy some time, so
escape on your own... Our friends should be here
soon...
I-I'm sorry... I promise to come back for help...
